15. Qg4 g6 16. Bh6 Qe7 17. Bg5 f6
{ Blacks barrier is very tenacious and hard to break down. } 18. Re1 O-O-O
{ Of course not   18...fxg5  19.Rxe6  +- } 19. Bd2
{ The game continuation relies on the fact that   19.Rxe6 ??  Qd7  would lose material as in fact g5 and e6 are hanging, e.g.  20.Bd2  Nc7  21.Bb3  Rhe8  -+ }
